comment: On the post/prenup, Johnny had tried to get the prenup before they married.  He again tried to get a post nup when they were in Australia when he was filming pirates of the Caribbean. That was the reason for the fight that resulted in his having his finger cut off and the bone broken.  According to Amber's audio (that she took w/no one's approval) she was on a cocktail of drugs, including a hallucinogen.  One thing abusers do is they raise a stink if you raise something they don't want you to raise.  For Amber, that was the post-nup.  She did not want to limit what she could get out of Johnny should the marriage fail.  So when he and his lawyer raised it. she threw such a big fit -- smashing bottles, breaking glass, etc -- that he would never raise that topic again.  End result, Johnny had his finger smashed and the tip cut off and he never got a post nup out of her.  Amber's claim that Johnny was on a 3 day drug-fueled bender is a lie.  Johnny was on set for two of those three days.  She was the one on the 3 day drug bender.  She was alone for two of those days, during which she painted a painting of Johnny.  Johnny could not have been on a drug bender while filming and he wasn't home for most of that time.  In the audio Amber recorded, she admitted to cutting of the tip of Johnny's finger and she admitted to the range of drugs she was taking.  Her later stories were inconsistent with the audio.
